{"tid":473290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最佳國家品牌 德國踢下美國稱霸","createTime":"2017-11-19T05:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T12:19:06.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"57a49bf7964cebf50bb0468fbb62927a32a6ac41","tid":473290,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:59:23.000Z","msg":"全球最佳國家品牌 德國踢下美國稱霸<br />\n<br />\n根據全球最佳國家品牌排名調查，美國品牌在總統川普執政的時代下遭受重大打擊。去年美國在這份調查中稱冠，但今年一路滑到第6，德國則是今年的霸主。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）報導，安霍特捷孚凱國家品牌指數（Anholt-GfK Nation Brands Index）針對50個國家各個領域進行評估，包括政府治理、出口、文化、人民、觀光及移民與投資。<br />\n<br />\n10年多前創立這份品牌調查的政治顧問安霍特（Simon Anholt）說，美國會大退步的原因是川普。<br />\n<br />\n安霍特在聲明中表示：「在川普總統強調『美國優先』的政治訊息後，我們看到了『川普效應』。」<br />\n<br />\n安霍特指出，儘管美國名次在總排名大幅下滑，但跟去年比起來，受訪的美國民眾其實對自己國家的評價更加正面。<br />\n<br />\n而且今年也不是美國第一次在這份調查中名次慘跌。安霍特說，2004年總統小布希成功連任後，美國當年名次跌到第7。<br />\n<br />\n德國今年稱冠要拜政府治理、人民和文化領域分數大幅增加之賜。<br />\n<br />\n去年因公投脫離歐洲聯盟受到打擊的英國，今年奪回足夠的失地，穩住陣腳，依舊排名第3。<br />\n<br />\n法國位居第2；加拿大和日本並列第4；義大利第7；瑞士第8；澳洲第9；瑞典第10。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201711180063-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201711180063-1.aspx&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1c41dc4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201711180063-1.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"019f3518419cded651e1e28d709b1bab6afa06fc","tid":473290,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"原來一直都唔係德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6050d94d9da6376cb515f078c0de49b334f728","tid":473290,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"其實我從來未見過「國家品牌」嘅評分有美國份<br />\n頭十一定係德國、瑞士、英國、意大利、日本、歐盟，都唔知排到邊先到美國"},{"pid":"e1682599d44cb9c74daba2fcda6886c6ccf9a653","tid":473290,"uid":53172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"永遠唔會有支那份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70637887b57ce7f6eadde6d4b5c092cc1a6ed61f","tid":473290,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/141348_739ace398588d02d55272d2834f8272d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F141348_739ace398588d02d55272d2834f8272d.PNG&h=465de8fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c4ec0584171338e836a78d2fa017a309144ebf3","tid":473290,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"美國憑咩同德國爭"},{"pid":"bfdae075e50846657573dd3729f2f66cf288f784","tid":473290,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"引入咁多難民<br />\n唔知keep到幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c4a05cde64d4fff49e79243ad0550a81004719","tid":473290,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/141348_739ace398588d02d55272d2834f8272d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F141348_739ace398588d02d55272d2834f8272d.PNG&h=465de8fc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個表可以咁撚波動都唔方可靠啦"},{"pid":"48b57e5e672be2fdda290f723aa1238c1c6a296e","tid":473290,"uid":37584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永遠唔會有支那份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國明明係第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倒數第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gi